detail.name: AB
detail.public_notice: Newton Project (NEW) has rebranded to AB DAO (AB). For detailed information, kindly visit here.

description.en: AB (prev. Newton) is an advanced blockchain ecosystem evolving from the Newton Project, designed for decentralization, interoperability, and real-world asset (RWA) integration. It features a high-performance mainnet, industry-specific sidechains, and cross-chain compatibility with Ethereum, Solana, and other networks.

ico_data.short_desc: Newton provides blockchain infrastructure for the community economy.
